  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK611">
<l>arumai yuṭaitteṉ ṟacāvāmai vēṇṭum</l>
<l>perumai muyaṟci tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Yield not to the feebleness which says, "this is too difficult to be done"; labour will give the greatness (of mind) which is necessary (to do it).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
